<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Frequently Asked Questions - Tax Prep Expert</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
</head>

<style>
    /* FAQ Page */
    .faq-container {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 60px auto;
        padding: 30px;
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 16px;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
    }

    .faq-container h1 {
        font-size: 2.3rem;
        color: #2c3e50;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .faq-container .intro {
        text-align: center;
        color: #555;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .faq-item {
        margin-bottom: 25px;
        padding-bottom: 15px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
    }

    .faq-item h2 {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        color: #0077cc;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .faq-item p {
        font-size: 1rem;
        color: #444;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* Links inside FAQ */
    .faq-item a {
        color: #0077cc;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
    }

    .faq-item a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
    }

    .back-home {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 30px;
    }

    /* Back to Sitemap Button */
    .back-sitemap {
        text-align: center;
        /* center the button */
        margin: 40px 0;
        /* space above and below */
    }

    .back-sitemap a {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 12px 28px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff7e5f, #feb47b);
        /* warm gradient */
        color: #fff;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 30px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(255, 126, 95, 0.3);
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .back-sitemap a:hover {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e55d3f, #fd9e50);
        transform: translateY(-3px);
        box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(255, 126, 95, 0.4);
    }

    .back-sitemap a:active {
        transform: translateY(1px);
        box-shadow: 0 3px 8px rgba(255, 126, 95, 0.4);
    }

    footer {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 15px;
        background: #0077cc;
        color: white;
        margin-top: 40px;
        border-radius: 0 0 12px 12px;
    }
</style>

<body>
    <div class="faq-container">
        <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
        <p class="intro">Here are answers to some of the most common questions about our tax preparation services.</p>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <h2>1. What documents do I need to bring for tax preparation?</h2>
            <p>You’ll need your W-2s, 1099s, prior year tax returns, Social Security numbers for all dependents, and any
                receipts related to deductions (such as education, childcare, or medical expenses).</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <h2>2. How long does a typical tax preparation appointment take?</h2>
            <p>Most appointments take 45–90 minutes depending on the complexity of your return. Business filings or
                multiple income sources may take longer.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <h2>3. Can you file my taxes electronically?</h2>
            <p>Yes, we offer secure electronic filing (e-file) for both federal and state returns. You’ll get
                confirmation when your return is accepted.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <h2>4. Do you offer virtual/remote appointments?</h2>
            <p>Absolutely. You can upload your documents securely online and schedule a virtual consultation with one of
                our tax professionals.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <h2>5. How much do your tax preparation services cost?</h2>
            <p>Pricing depends on the type of return. Individual returns start at $130, married filing jointly at $150,
                and business returns vary. Visit our <a href="/pricing">Pricing Page</a> for details.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <h2>6. How do I book an appointment?</h2>
            <p>You can easily <a href="/book-an-appointment">book an appointment online</a> through our scheduling
                system or call our office.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
            <h2>7. What if I need to amend a previous tax return?</h2>
            <p>We can help you file an amended return if you need to correct errors or add information to a previously
                filed return.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="back-sitemap">
            <a href="/sitemap">⬅ Back to Sitemap</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

<footer>
    <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Tax Prep Expert. All rights reserved.</p>

</footer>
</html>